Limpeza de metadados quando um controlador de dominio tive escrachado, executar via ntdsutil.

limpeza de metadados:

Abri o CMD e executar o ntdsutil e seguir os passos abaixo:

ntdsutil: metadata cleanup

metadata cleanup: connections

server connection: connect to domian xxxx.corp

server connection: q

metadata cleanup: select operation target

select operation target: list domains

select operation target: selecy doamin 0

select operation target: list site

select operation target: select site 0

select operation target: list servers in site

select operation target: select server 2

select operation target: q

metadata cleanup: remove seelcted server
